Content:
Look forward to meeting soon ! Can you let us know when you are able to meet in the Bay
Area in the next couple of days ?

I land in San Jose tomorrow around 2pm and depart around midnight . My Tesla meetings are
flexible , so I can meet anytime in those 10 hours .
By " tomorrow " do you mean Thursday or Friday ?
Today
I can make any time in those 10 hours work .

I land in Oakland at 8:30 pm . Perhaps we can meet at 9:30 pm somewhere ? I am working to
see if I can move up my flight from NYC to land earlier in the meantime

Working on landing earlier and landing in San Jose so we can have dinner near you . Will keep
you both posted in real time

Ok , successfully moved my flight to land at 6:30 pm in San Jose . Working on a place we can
meet privately
Sounds good

Crypto spam on Twitter really needs to get crushed . It's a major blight on the user experience
and they scam so many innocent people .

It sounds like we are confirming 7pm at a private residence near San Jose . Our assistants
reached out to Jehn on logistics . Let me know if either of you have any concerns or want to
move things around . Looking forward to our conversation .
Works for me . Excited to see you both in person !
Jehn had a baby and I decided to try having no assistant for a few months
Likewise
The address is
Does 7pm work for you Elon ?
Probably close to that time . Might only be able to get there by 7:30 , but will try for earlier .

Sounds good . I am going to be a bit early because my plane is landing earlier but free all
evening so we can start whenever you get there and Parag and I can catch up in the meantime

This wins for the weirdest place I've had a meeting recently . I think they were looking for an
airbnb near the airport and there are tractors and donkeys
Haha awesome
Maybe Airbnb's algorithm thinks you love tractors and donkeys ( who doesn't ! )
On my way . There in about 15 mins .
And abandoned trucks in case we want to start a catering business after we meet
Sounds like a post - apocalyptic movie set
Basically yes
Great dinner :)

Definitely one for the memory books haha
Memorable for multiple reasons . Really enjoyed it
